    "desc": "REIKI: International Association of Reiki Professionals – The #1 Resource for Reiki Worldwide. Enjoy the AMAZING BENEFITS Professional Reiki Memberships offer.",
    "navbar": "",
    "text": "Skip to content\nIARP, Celebrating over 25 years of loving service to members in over 50 countries - BECOME AN IARP MEMBER TODAY!\nFacebook\nTwitter\nYouTube\nIARP helps you\nshareyo\nTOGETHER WE CAN DO SO MUCH MORE!\nLEARN MORE ABOUT IARP\nSEARCH\nFind a Reiki Healer or Reiki Master Teacher near you. The IARP Locator features thousands of gifted Registered Reiki Healing Practitioners and Reiki Master Teachers in over 50 countries!\nCLICK HERE TO START YOUR SEARCH\nSUCCEED\nIARP helps new and established Reiki Healers and Reiki Master Teachers start and grow their practices. Our business and marketing tools are essential to a thriving Reiki business. Join IARP today!\nGET LOVING SUPPORT FOR YOUR REIKI PRACTICE\nYOU, YOUR FAMILY, YOUR PETS\nreiki is for everyone\nREIKI FOR ALL LIFE STAGES\nIARP is for Growth, Success, and Community\nCelebrating over 25 years of loving service to members in over 50 countries, we look forward to you enjoying world-class benefits and being a valued part of the global Reiki healing community. We help you grow, succeed and flourish with your beautiful work in the world with Reiki and other beneficial modalities. Reach more clients and students, be your best, be all that you were meant to be.\nIARP Registered Professional Membership is open to all Independent Reiki Healing Practitioners and Master Teachers in all countries. Learn about Reiki Insurance, Reiki Certificates, and other invaluable resources and business tools you can enjoy as a Registered Professional Member of IARP.\nSEE ALL OUR AMAZING BENEFITS!\nRead our most-loved articles\nIARP IS ALL ABOUT YOU!\nREIKI SENSATIONS\nCHAKRA BASICS\nSEE ALL REIKI ARTICLES AND POSTS\nReiki and Medicine\nHospitals, medical centers and facilities, hospices, and physicians in private practice are utilizing healing Reiki therapy as a beneficial complement to their professional services. Ask your primary health care provider how Reiki may benefit you (and their work) as part of a health, healing, or wellness plan.\nLearn how Reiki can help Chronic Fatigue, Headaches and Migraines, Asthma, Anxiety Disorders, Insomnia, Depression, and much more.\nREAD ARTICLES ABOUT REIKI IN MEDICINE\nTHE #1 RESOURCE FOR REIKI. WORLDWIDE.\nCelebrating over 25 years of Loving Service to the global Reiki Community.\nJOIN IARP TODAY!\n© Copyright 1996 - 2022 IARP | All Rights Reserved",
    "font": "\"Open Sans\", Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif",
